title: Sawbones: Charcoal
description:
Grilling season is over in our part of the U.S. and Justin wants to know what he's gonna do with all this left over charcoal. The answer, according to Dr. Sydnee? EVERYTHING.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
